title: Gente Nova
body: The first issue was released on October 15, 1919, and the last, the tenth, on March 20, 1920. It was published again in February 1921. It was a newspaper written by high school students.

1919: Start of the publication of the Gente Nova newspaper
1920: End of the first publication of the Gente Nova newspaper
1921: Resumption of the publication of the Gente Nova newspaper
